@Node "FreeDB_GDDisc" "GetDisc"

  @{u}@{b}GetDisc@{ub}@{uu}


    The GetDisc application is used to retrieve disc information
    in async way.

    It's window opens iff the disc can't be found or multi
    matches were found.

    If a disc can't be found locally, it lets you control the
    connection to the freedb server.

    If multi matches are found it lets you choose among them.

@EndNode

